01:22:14,600 --> 01:22:15,600
Evan!

901
01:22:16,680 --> 01:22:17,680
Evan!

902
01:22:18,920 --> 01:22:20,206
Điều gì mà quan trọng như vậy?

903
01:22:22,960 --> 01:22:24,564
Tôi xin lỗi, Mike.

904
01:22:25,120 --> 01:22:26,120
Cái gì?

905
